{"tid":1266943,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"[由急症室返黎]肉體上根骨歪，會否影響心跳/心痿，發痺","createTime":"2019-06-29T16:35:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T12:54:19.000Z","uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"42f555f1c28ef1e347557d7bc22b7e2df049da76","tid":1266943,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:35:20.000Z","msg":"長年姿勢問題，根骨唔正，頭先亂拉根，全身少少痺，扯實<br />\n然後心跳加速，身體顫抖，手腳冰冷，全身毛管洞<br />\n醫緊思覺失調5年<br />\n做心電圖，X光冇事<br />\n醫生話似焦慮，唔似肉體問題<br />\n叫我食齊舊藥，咩藥都冇開就算<br />\n<br />\n根骨肌肉唔正位置，會否影響心臟心跳等器官，發緊麻"},{"pid":"03bd283f1298639320db06d74f90f08442d0cd09","tid":1266943,"uid":99582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:36:48.000Z","msg":"有聽過頸有問題會影響 會影響交感神經"},{"pid":"dc0cea266b270e32f32376365d196e865ee73d60","tid":1266943,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03bd283f1298639320db06d74f90f08442d0cd09","tid":1266943,"uid":99582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:36:48.000Z","msg":"有聽過頸有問題會影響 會影響交感神經"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:39:04.000Z","msg":"我坐著時，左邊屁股扯實唔舒服<br />\n而家係心恐，全身毛管洞"},{"pid":"1cd533811ffbce006c0639fa194704cd701ea0e0","tid":1266943,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:45:00.000Z","msg":"個心係怕就死，個人呼吸有少少震/痙攣"},{"pid":"c8ec1644c936f53468a5e359de8bae6c7aaa7915","tid":1266943,"uid":99582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc0cea266b270e32f32376365d196e865ee73d60","tid":1266943,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03bd283f1298639320db06d74f90f08442d0cd09","tid":1266943,"uid":99582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:36:48.000Z","msg":"有聽過頸有問題會影響 會影響交感神經"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:39:04.000Z","msg":"我坐著時，左邊屁股扯實唔舒服<br />\n而家係心恐，全身毛管洞"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:46:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/health/5j9n62.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fk